   "content": [
      {
         "id": "2923834e-bf4b-4d92-adad-c581b00ccf3d",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\">Nesta fase, seu objetivo é buscar respostas e compreender as etapas do método científico (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('44acb900-ee84-4e42-8d9b-a947351af2cd'); return false;\">History Tracers (<span class=\"htdate\"></span>): Scientific Method</a>).</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\">Nas ciências, quando temos uma ideia, devemos testá-la para verificar se ela explica algo. A ciência não é sobre aceitar sem questionamento, nem sobre acreditar em algo cegamente e rejeitar o oposto. A ciência é um processo contínuo de aprendizado e descoberta.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": null,
         "next": "66cf7457-cc81-4c29-8c20-48a4136a9bcb",
         "prev": "",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": null,
         "score": 1
      },
      {
         "id": "66cf7457-cc81-4c29-8c20-48a4136a9bcb",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<span class=\"smGameTextTitleSize\">Apresentação</span><p class=\"smGameTextSize\">Vamos verificar se as figuras abaixo, que possuem as mesmas larguras e alturas, são iguais.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><table class=\"tawapukllay\" style=\"width: 50%;\"><tr><th>Quadrado</th><th>Círculo</th></tr> <tr><td><div class=\"square\" style=\"background-color:lightblue;width:5.5vw;height:5.5vw\"></div></td> <td><i class=\"fa-solid fa-circle\" style=\"color:#FFCCCB;font-size:6vw;\"></i></td></tr></table></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": null,
         "next": "55aed802-158f-4144-9b45-ad44aa674368",
         "prev": "2923834e-bf4b-4d92-adad-c581b00ccf3d",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": null,
         "score": 1
      },
      {
         "id": "55aed802-158f-4144-9b45-ad44aa674368",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\">Nosso primeiro passo é criar uma pergunta:</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection_parent\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection smGameTextSize\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection question_mark\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-brain\"></i></div><div class=\"first_steps_reflection\"><b>Sobre a igualdade</b><br />Um quadrado e um círculo são iguais?</div></div></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": null,
         "next": "dc635f7b-cc08-498f-81a6-5ff52266ac62",
         "prev": "66cf7457-cc81-4c29-8c20-48a4136a9bcb",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": null,
         "score": 1
      },
      {
         "id": "dc635f7b-cc08-498f-81a6-5ff52266ac62",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\">Precisamos definir as hipóteses, ou seja, as possíveis respostas que queremos testar:</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><b>HIPÓTESE 1</b>: As figuras são iguais.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><b>HIPÓTESE 2</b>: As figuras são diferentes.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\">Vamos realizar alguns testes para chegar à <b>teoria</b>, ou resposta desejada (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('44acb900-ee84-4e42-8d9b-a947351af2cd'); return false;\">History Tracers (<span class=\"htdate\"></span>): Scientific Method</a>).</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": null,
         "next": "062a5626-0e1f-4cc4-88b6-7b4128503dfd",
         "prev": "55aed802-158f-4144-9b45-ad44aa674368",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": null,
         "score": 1
      },
      {
         "id": "062a5626-0e1f-4cc4-88b6-7b4128503dfd",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<span class=\"smGameTextTitleSize\">Comparando partes</span><p class=\"smGameTextSize\">Vamos colocar uma parte do círculo sobre uma parte do quadrado.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><div class=\"desc\"><div class=\"square\" style=\"width:3vw;height:3vw;background-color:lightblue;\"><div class=\"quartercircle\" style=\"width:3vw;height:3vw;background-color:#FFCCCB;\"></div></div></div></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection_parent\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection smGameTextSize\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection question_mark\">?</div><div class=\"first_steps_reflection\"><b>As partes</b><br />A parte do círculo cobre completamente a parte do quadrado?</div></div></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": [
            "Ao usar apenas partes do mesmo tamanho, é possível ver parte do quadrado."
         ],
         "next": "9521d6ae-79f8-4cdd-95e4-05bc56a6a301",
         "prev": "dc635f7b-cc08-498f-81a6-5ff52266ac62",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": 0,
         "score": 2
      },
      {
         "id": "9521d6ae-79f8-4cdd-95e4-05bc56a6a301",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<span class=\"smGameTextTitleSize\">Comparando as figuras</span><p class=\"smGameTextSize\">Agora, vamos sobrepor as figuras completas uma sobre a outra.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><div class=\"desc\"><div class=\"square\" style=\"width:6vw;height:6vw;background-color:lightblue;\"><div class=\"circle\" style=\"width:6vw;height:6vw;background-color:#FFCCCB;\"></div></div></div></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection_parent\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection smGameTextSize\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection question_mark\">?</div><div class=\"first_steps_reflection\"><b>O todo</b><br />O círculo cobre completamente o quadrado?</div></div></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": [
            "Com as figuras completas, ainda é possível ver parte do quadrado."
         ],
         "next": "a3951d7c-99ed-45bc-9f73-ad0e601fd179",
         "prev": "062a5626-0e1f-4cc4-88b6-7b4128503dfd",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": 0,
         "score": 2
      },
      {
         "id": "a3951d7c-99ed-45bc-9f73-ad0e601fd179",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<span class=\"smGameTextTitleSize\">Tabelando</span><p class=\"smGameTextSize\">Após os experimentos, organizamos os resultados em uma tabela para comparação:</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><table class=\"indigenous_period\"><tr><th>Experimentos</th><th>Figuras iguais</th><th>Figuras diferentes</th></tr> <tr><th>Partes de figuras</th><td>&nbsp;</td><td><b>X</b></td></tr> <tr><th>Figuras completas</th><td>&nbsp;</td><td><b>X</b></td></tr> </table>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection_parent\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection smGameTextSize\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection question_mark\">?</div><div class=\"first_steps_reflection\"><b>Sobre os resultados</b><br />Comparando os resultados, podemos dizer que as figuras são diferentes?</div></div></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": [
            "Com base nos resultados, podemos concluir que as figuras são diferentes."
         ],
         "next": "2ad76f9a-1d5c-4b2c-9a34-3b9edfdf3fed",
         "prev": "9521d6ae-79f8-4cdd-95e4-05bc56a6a301",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": 1,
         "score": 2
      },
      {
         "id": "2ad76f9a-1d5c-4b2c-9a34-3b9edfdf3fed",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<span class=\"smGameTextTitleSize\">A teoria (1/2)</span><p class=\"smGameTextSize\">Inicialmente, trabalhamos com duas hipóteses:</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><b>HIPÓTESE 1</b>: As figuras são iguais.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><b>HIPÓTESE 2</b>: As figuras são diferentes.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": null,
         "next": "a3c919d2-5e7e-4895-a830-81958c7ea473",
         "prev": "",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": 1,
         "score": 1
      },
      {
         "id": "a3c919d2-5e7e-4895-a830-81958c7ea473",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<span class=\"smGameTextTitleSize\">A teoria (2/2)</span><p class=\"smGameTextSize\">Após os experimentos, podemos desconsiderar a <b>HIPÓTESE 1</b> e desenvolver a <b>teoria</b> de que um quadrado é diferente de um círculo, conforme demonstrado no método científico (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('44acb900-ee84-4e42-8d9b-a947351af2cd'); return false;\">History Tracers (<span class=\"htdate\"></span>): Scientific Method</a>).</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><center><i class=\"fa-solid fa-medal\" style=\"color:gold; font-size: 5vw\"></i></center></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": null,
         "next": "",
         "prev": "",
